////////How to publish Website in GitHub///////////////////////////////

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OltY8JIaP-4

How to publish Personal Website (like portfolio)
--------------------------------------------
Step-1 : Login to your github account

Step-2: Create a new Repositories

- click on "New" button
- Repository name: yourusername.github.io
- Add a README file
- click on "Create repository" button 

Step-3: Upload website files (index.html, about.html,...) with css files in your repository

Step-4: Change Settings
- click on "Settings" link --> Pages
	- Source: Master/Main
	- click on Save
- you will see website access url. copy the url and paste in browser


How to publish Other Website
--------------------------------
Step-1 : Login to your github account

Step-2: Create a new Repositories

- click on "New" button
- Repository name: yourProjectName
- Add a README file
- click on "Create repository" button 

Step-3: Upload website files (index.html, about.html,...) with css files in your repository

Step-4: Change Settings
- click on "Settings" link --> Pages
	- Source: Master/Main
	- click on Save
- you will see website access url. copy the url and paste in browser


index.html
----------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale-1.0"> <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
<title>MAIN PAGE</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<h1>Welcome to my Personal Website!</h1>
<h2>Check out my youtube channel for web game tutorials!</h2> 
<h2>Don't forget to like and subscribe to my youtube channel!</h2> 
<a href="./about"> <h2>Click here to learn about me!</h2></a> </div>
</body> 
</html>

about.html
---------------
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale-1.0"> <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"
<title>ABOUT PAGE</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<h1>ABOUT ME</h1>
<p>Hi, I'm Kenny and I teach coding on youtube!</p>
<a href="./"> <h2>Click here to return to main page!</h2></a>
</div>
/body
</html>





